{"tid":623291,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"完全睇唔到將來..","createTime":"2018-04-10T01:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T10:48:46.000Z","uid":173453,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fa649d2318029e61192e8d5a81eccfa53c9bb65a","tid":623291,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:21:32.000Z","msg":"90後一名<br />\n近呢兩年好勤力番工<br />\n而且毒撚又無乜洗費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加上得閒行下啲狗屎運係馬會到中下波<br />\n而家終於都叫有6位數係銀行<br />\n我知我都係得雞碎咁多<br />\n所以先想去增加下收入<br />\n又或者想自己搞下生意仔咁樣<br />\n但身邊啲朋友全部都係廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢地傾，佢地只係話好阿好阿，預埋我阿<br />\n都真係要起行果陣又話無咁多錢又話而家份工幾好<br />\n有啲寧願係屋企日日打機唔番工<br />\n我唔係話佢地錯<br />\n但點解後生仔可以完全無上進心<br />\n打份10k工作就滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係唔想咁，俾身邊啲朋友搞到好頹<br />\n近呢兩年成日番工已經俾佢地話我掛住搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係想疏遠佢地<br />\n但如果咁做又無晒啲朋友<br />\n(因為以前的關係,本身已經唔多朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n我唔知我係咪真係掛住搵錢<br />\n我淨係知無錢係無辦法生存..<br />\n有無啲巴打交流下可以俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da63b66d46c06a306dfebca4d5f64bcdf10915f","tid":623291,"uid":139676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"Be fd?ok?"},{"pid":"9fa3ef5a781a6a5c528a11cd61e7953cb6996f0e","tid":623291,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"打份10k工, 明顯係排緊公屋啦<br />\n無論排單人定家庭"},{"pid":"2fa5ff7aeb57f1fa26696d667fb16486300589f5","tid":623291,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9da63b66d46c06a306dfebca4d5f64bcdf10915f","tid":623291,"uid":139676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"Be fd?ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:30:13.000Z","msg":"Ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba18f2cf01f783015139fc73cd658458f94bf9a3","tid":623291,"uid":173453,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa3ef5a781a6a5c528a11cd61e7953cb6996f0e","tid":623291,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"打份10k工, 明顯係排緊公屋啦<br />\n無論排單人定家庭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"我有問過<br />\n佢地無排到公屋<br />\n因為有知佢屋企本身住緊所以佢話無排<br />\n另外果個就強調佢屋企人有樓留俾佢<br />\n10k係貪工時短唔辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f2eebed420e9b15e26bb06d6d667170cca1ae5","tid":623291,"uid":118428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"be fd ok?<br />\ntell me what u wanna do then count on me"},{"pid":"cbfeb28e554d959fdd2b88392ffc9e3566cb9a92","tid":623291,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"樓主有做大事既性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比心gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baa995ff22bdd1e1f259737078027413f994359","tid":623291,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f2eebed420e9b15e26bb06d6d667170cca1ae5","tid":623291,"uid":118428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"be fd ok?<br />\ntell me what u wanna do then count on me"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:42:20.000Z","msg":"Ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba97aa26c594795a70ca019928137845ad3b4165","tid":623291,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbfeb28e554d959fdd2b88392ffc9e3566cb9a92","tid":623291,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"樓主有做大事既性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比心gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl